{"tid":2373067,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聽障青年好奇撿5枚棄置催淚彈殼收藏 判12個月感化令","createTime":"2021-01-20T07:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T18:00:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4e06766601065dce22f12d5d02d61e173239fd88","tid":2373067,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13078&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia0WuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=160d80d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13078</a><br />\n<br />\n#沙田裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#溫紹明署理主任裁判官 <br />\n#判刑<br />\n#1115沙田<br />\n<br />\n馬（23）<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n無牌管有彈藥<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月15日在大圍車公廟路及翠田街交界近燈柱EB2756，管有5枚已發射之CS催淚彈彈殻，而沒有持有該彈藥的管有權及經營人牌照。<br />\n<br />\n求情：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11219&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia0WuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=ab84ee1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11219</a><br />\n上次進度：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11967&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia0WuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=d754bd90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11967</a><br />\n<br />\n被告願意接受並明白感化<br />\n<br />\n法庭接納被告犯案是出於好奇，沒動機傷害人，指被告有特殊背景，因私隱問題而不會在庭上指出。本案不涉及群眾活動，沒有人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n🔴12個月感化<br />\n。要聽從感化官指示交友,工作，守財政指示<br />\n。參與對更生有助的職業訓練,評估"},{"pid":"531f1f0e04c73cd0516b4be136df4151e8b3e79b","tid":2373067,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:34:38.000Z","msg":"聽障青年因一時好奇，前年在街上撿起5枚催淚彈彈殼收藏，凌晨時份獨自街上流連時遭警方截查揭發。青年早前承認一項無牌管有彈藥罪，溫紹明裁判官今判刑時稱，本案雖控罪嚴重，但案情相對輕微，因為涉案彈藥已不能使用，故接納並無傷人動機，亦不能與其他較嚴重的社運案件相提並論，終判被告接受12個月感化令。<br />\n<br />\n溫官又指，被告的個人情況特殊，令他需花較長時間才能掌握犯罪後果及法律程序，但相信他現在已經理解及明白到案件的嚴重性。溫官認為感化令對被告有正面幫助，要求他在感化期間，須按感化官指示工作、居住或作財政安排，以及參加與職業培訓有關的活動。"},{"pid":"6fcc1567cf214e28bfa11f9443dcf0fbf10f1aa5","tid":2373067,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ab88a139b8066c1dd03fa8bf718ccdad762892","tid":2373067,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fcc1567cf214e28bfa11f9443dcf0fbf10f1aa5","tid":2373067,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b687d384a7f6fa79962c5277614b65c8237f6a","tid":2373067,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3ab88a139b8066c1dd03fa8bf718ccdad762892","tid":2373067,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fcc1567cf214e28bfa11f9443dcf0fbf10f1aa5","tid":2373067,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3585edde439a67bd5a0821c62856dfc5c7e3fc2b","tid":2373067,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"溫官 少數正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072ebc246809d4d5f8455c7e9578531ee42e9e81","tid":2373067,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987510e385234e8c0c0722a6c5a57059d65f7a4a","tid":2373067,"uid":51271,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:48:27.000Z","msg":"粒野已經無晒效，班狗唔執等你執果時先去咬，佢老味"},{"pid":"42d95d6e6c31c34ce67ff32f189087336d3d5347","tid":2373067,"uid":178459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288ec86bd41e68be77415cab65b74c9162ce5425","tid":2373067,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea1f0aa1d114c4f0ad3bea5442d999179f338a4","tid":2373067,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:53:00.000Z","msg":"父母雙亡的獨居聽障青年，前年11月凌晨在街頭遇上警員截查，被搜出藏有5枚已發射過的催淚彈彈殼。青年早前承認無牌管有彈藥罪，案件今在沙田裁判法院判刑。署理主任裁判官溫紹明判刑時指，涉案彈殼經已使用，不能傷人，與較嚴重的同類案件不能相提並論。溫官接納被告犯案只是出於好奇，並強調被告背景特殊，「需要比別人花多少少時間理解犯案後果以及法庭程序」，最終判青年接受感化令12個月。<br />\n<br />\n警方化驗證實彈殼已無爆炸性或毒性，不能重用或再發射。<br />\n<br />\n署理主任裁判官溫紹明今判刑前主動詢問被告：「你聽得清楚我哋講嘢㗎嘛？」被告點頭示意聽得見。辯方續引述報告指，被告明確表示願意接受感化，建議法庭採納報告建議。<br />\n<br />\n溫官判刑時指，雖然控罪嚴重，但涉案催淚彈殼經已使用，與同類案件有所區別。溫官接納被告是因出於好奇而執拾彈殼，沒有任何動機使用，「彈殼本身都唔能夠用，更遑論去傷害人」。<br />\n<br />\n溫官強調被告個人情況特殊，接納被告需要比別人多花時間去理解法庭程序及犯罪後果，且考慮到案中無人受傷、不涉及暴力或群眾活動，判處被告接受感化令12個月，其間須跟從感化官指示，接受職業培訓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/QGAFJZDARVEMRFQPYJIKJRHBBQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2FQGAFJZDARVEMRFQPYJIKJRHBBQ%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia0WuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=8aeec850\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2FQGAFJZDARVEMRFQPYJIKJRHBBQ%2F&h=81b93d92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/QGAFJZDARVEMRFQPYJIKJRHBBQ/</a>"},{"pid":"c253621274f2fa401eb89c0ebcd19833b92faf28","tid":2373067,"uid":189234,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"溫官好有人情味<img src=\"/assets/faces